                    "faIcon": null,
                    "faIconColors": {
                        "bg": "",
                        "fill": ""
                    },
                    "locales": {
                        "en": {
                            "text": "<p>I'm a <b>Software Development Engineer</b> at <b>Jio Platforms</b>, specializing in [[backend engineering]] and distributed systems. I build large-scale, fault-tolerant infrastructure using {{Go}}, Kubernetes, and event-driven architectures.</p><p>I designed and implemented a <b>Data Center Infrastructure Management</b> system managing 10,000+ servers, an <b>IP Address Management</b> service automating IPv4/IPv6 allocation, and a <b>centralized IAM system</b> using OAuth2/OIDC and OpenFGA across 5+ services.</p><p>I'm passionate about [[clean architecture]], system design, and building things that scale reliably under pressure.</p>"
                        }
                    }
                }
            ]
